props.description:
Transit distance and duration, can take one of the following values:

`here` - use HERE Large Matrix API (must be enabled for user account);
`osrm` - (default) use OpenStreetMap and Open Source Routing Machine without traffic;

Other types of transit matrices and traffic support is available only via API.

Route planning quality, can take one of the following values:

- `debug` - quick optimization mode, recommended for request debugging and data integrity validation;
- `normal` - (default) regular quality of optimization;
- `high` - high quality of optimization (incurs additional cost and waiting time);

